3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses recurrent neural networks to generate cinemagraph sequences. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating animations from still images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating cinemagraphs, which are a form of multimedia content.
